<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="K" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Kneel" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Kneel</orth> (impf. and part. <emph>--ed</emph>) to bend the knee: <bibl n="shak. luc 1830" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1830</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 2, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.4.81" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 4, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.93.81" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.93.81" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 93</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.162" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. V, 2, 162</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.153" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 153</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.310" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 310</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.59" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 59</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.103" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 2, 103</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>our knees shall k.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.106" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 106</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a --ing knee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.106" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 106</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>to k. down:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 350" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 350</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.439" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 439</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.63" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.57" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.78" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 48</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>to k. at a person's feet:</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.140" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 140</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.194" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 194</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.107" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 161</bibl>. <emph>to k. before</emph> a p.: <bibl n="shak. mm 5.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 1, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 54</bibl>. <cit><quote>to k. down before:</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 44</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.5.150" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 5, 150</bibl>. <cit><quote>to k. to:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.128" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 128</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.123" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.129" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 129</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.177" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 5, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.162" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 162</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 21</bibl> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.417" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 417</bibl> etc.
